    <refsection id="Description_SIGNUM">
        <title>Description</title>
        <para>
            The block output is a vector of the signs of the elements of the input vector.
            For each input vector's element, the output vector's element is:
        </para>
        <itemizedlist>
            <listitem>
                <para> 1 when the element is greater than zero.</para>
            </listitem>
            <listitem>
                <para> 0 when the element is equal to zero.</para>
            </listitem>
            <listitem>
                <para> -1 when the element is less than zero.</para>
            </listitem>
        </itemizedlist>
    </refsection>
